<h1 id="about-me">About Me</h1>

<p>Studied the wonders of course <a href="http://www.eecs.mit.edu">6</a> and <a href="http://web.mit.edu/be">20</a> while at <a href="http://www.mit.edu">MIT</a>. Co-founded a <a href="http://benchling.com">bioinformatics startup</a> after graduation. Now a game designer &amp; product engineer at <a href="http://sizigistudios.com">Sizigi Studios</a>.</p>

<p>Random domain knowledge in graphics, <a href="http://www.cstarleague.com">esports</a>, and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Synthetic_biology">synthetic biology</a>.</p>

<p>Best way to reach me is through <a href="https://twitter.com/cixelyn">twitter</a>. Barring that there&rsquo;s also <a href="http://www.facebook.com/coryli">facebook</a>, <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=82675650">linkedin</a>, and <a href="https://bitbucket.org/Cixelyn">bitbucket</a> (although I hear this <a href="https://github.com/cixelyn">github</a> thing is pretty popular too :p)</p>

